              "textEn": "Bak is ill for two weeks. In that time, Hapu makes a lot of tables and chairs. But only tables and chairs. He makes a gold necklace, too. \"There!\" he thinks late one night. \"It's ready. He smiles. The necklace is very beautiful. \"Queen Cleopatra is going to like this, \"Hapu thinks. \"She's going to pay a lot of money for it, too. I know she is.\""
