          "imgAlt": "A guard visits Hapu.",
          "imgPosition": "right",
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "That night Hapu looks up at the stars. \"Now I can pay for a doctor to visit father,\" he thinks. \"Then, after the father is strong again ... \" But at that moment he stops. One of Cleopatra's guards is standing in front of him. He has a big sword. \"Are you Hapu, son of Bak?\" he asks. Hapu looks at him. \"Yes. Yes, I am,\" he answers."
