          "imgPosition": "right",
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "\"Come with me,\" says the guard. \"Queen Cleopatra likes your work. She wants to give you a job at the palace.\" \"But I have a job,\" Hapu says. \"I work with my father. I can't leave him. You don't underst ...\" No, You don't understand,\" the guard says. \"When the Queen gives you a job, you take it.\" He puts one hand on his sword. \"Now go and say goodbye to your father.\""
