          "imgPosition": "right",
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "At the palace, Cleopatra talks to Hapu. She is wearing his necklace. \"I want you to live here and make lots of beautiful things for me,\" she says. \"Thank you, Queen, of the Nile,\" Hapu says. \"But ...\" \"But?\" The Queen looks at Hapu. \"But ... I can't live here. You see, my father is very ill and ...\" Hapu tells the Queen everything."
